seoHomeDescription: Tatjana Neufeld is a leading figure in today's classical music world. She is a Pianist, Chamber Musician. Accompanist and Keyboard Player
seoPodyomovaDescription: Next to solo performance, T. Neufeld gives piano lessons to children and involves herself in didactic practices
seoPartnershipsDescription: Next to solo performance T.Neufeld also stars in partnerships with other concert performers. Frequent concerts with different concert performers. See for Partnerships
landing_section_subheading: Piano stories of a Russian maestro
